Package pw.ollie.politics.command.args

Class Argument

  • java.lang.Object
    • pw.ollie.politics.command.args.Argument
  • public final class Argument
extends Object
    A wrapper around a String which allows for parsing of many primitive data types as well as providing methods to check whether the argument is a valid form of said primitive types.

    Argument objects are immutable and any methods which may appear to make a modification(s) to the state of the Argument will return a new object.
